        "abstract": "This document defines requirements for IPv6 nodes. It is expected that IPv6 will be deployed in a wide range of devices and situations. Specifying the requirements for IPv6 nodes allows IPv6 to function well and interoperate in a large number of situations and deployments.\n\n This document obsoletes RFC 6434, and in turn RFC 4294.",
