        "abstract": "The IETF Administration Support Activity (IASA) is responsible for arranging the selection and operation of the IETF plenary meeting venue.  This memo specifies IETF community requirements for meeting venues, including hotels and meeting space.  It also directs the IASA to make available additional process documents that describe the current meeting selection process.",
