        "formats": [],
        "abstract": "This memo describes a Transport Security Model for the Simple Network Management Protocol (SNMP).\n\n This memo also defines a portion of the Management Information Base (MIB) for monitoring and managing the Transport Security Model for SNMP. [STANDARDS-TRACK]",
        "text": "",
